y-is-speed"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062120","id":"zettel.20260420062120","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1246},"end":{"line":21,"column":52,"offset":1295},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062120","id":"zettel.20260420062120","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420060847","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1346},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1371},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":3,"offset":4283},"end":{"line":55,"column":28,"offset":4308},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420062120"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1254},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1279},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420062120"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420085220","id":"zettel.20260420085220","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1162},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1187},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420062120"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":62,"column":3,"offset":4448},"end":{"line":62,"column":28,"offset":4473},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420062120"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"cruft-adalah-utang-kebingungan-yang-memperlambat-perubahan\">Cruft adalah utang kebingungan yang memperlambat perubahan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#cruft-adalah-utang-kebingungan-yang-memperlambat-perubahan\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"Architecture is a tricky subject for the customers and users of software products - as it isn't something they immediately perceive. But a poor architecture is a major contributor to the growth of cruft - elements of the software that impede the ability of developers to understand the software. Software that contains a lot of cruft is much harder to modify, leading to features that arrive more slowly and with more defects.\"</p>\n<p>Sumber: <a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/architecture/\">https://martinfowler.com/architecture/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fowler mengatakan arsitektur yang buruk jarang terlihat langsung oleh pengguna, tetapi dampaknya nyata bagi developer dan delivery.</li>\n<li>Cruft adalah lapisan kekacauan yang menghambat pemahaman kode.</li>\n<li>Ketika software susah dipahami, perubahan menjadi lambat dan defect lebih sering muncul.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cruft bukan hanya technical debt umum; dia adalah \"utang kebingungan\" yang membuat tim semakin ragu saat menyentuh sistem.</li>\n<li>Mengurangi cruft adalah cara praktis menjaga kecepatan perubahan jangka panjang.</li>\n<li>Arsitektur yang baik harus mencegah akumulasi cruft dengan membuat sistem lebih mudah dipahami.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.internal-quality-is-speed\">Kualitas internal adalah infrastruktur kecepatan delivery</a> — literatur Fowler yang menekankan internal quality dan kecepatan delivery</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a> — ringkasan halaman Software Architecture Guide</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420060847\">Arsitektur adalah penentu biaya perubahan masa depan</a> — arsitektur sebagai penentu biaya perubahan masa depan</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">martin-fowler (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">cruft (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420062331\">Internal quality adalah infrastruktur kecepatan delivery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420085220\">Shortcut kualitas adalah pinjaman dari masa depan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"creat